1
00:00:36,736 --> 00:00:39,488
=Love Behind the Mask=

2
00:00:39,744 --> 00:00:41,312
=Episode 28=

3
00:00:41,888 --> 00:00:44,576
♪Willows ride the wind,
fish play among the lotuses♪

4
00:00:44,832 --> 00:00:47,648
♪You pluck the strings of my heart♪

5
00:00:47,904 --> 00:00:50,912
♪Eyes linger where emotions stir♪

6
00:00:52,159 --> 00:00:53,520
It's you again.

7
00:00:54,464 --> 00:00:57,248
♪Flowers bloom for a season
and wither overnight♪

8
00:00:57,248 --> 00:01:00,064
♪Hastily comes the farewell♪

9
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:02,280
Why are you here again?

10
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,600
I want to see you.

11
00:01:05,359 --> 00:01:06,640
When there's no one downstairs,

12
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:07,680
you should leave.

13
00:01:07,959 --> 00:01:09,120
Don't let anyone see you.

14
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:09,959
I won't leave.

15
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:11,120
Wangyou?

16
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:13,159
Wangyou?

17
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,560
Hide now.

18
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,200
Hurry.

19
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:31,879
Did someone come?

20
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:32,640
No.

21
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,359
Why are you so nervous?

22
00:01:35,319 --> 00:01:36,319
I painted a picture.

23
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,719
I'll go get it for you.

24
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:50,879
You...!

25
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:04,239
Lord of Zishang, it seems like
you treat my territory as your own turf.

26
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:06,599
First, you talked at length in my hall.

27
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:09,280
Now you've come here
to snatch my unwed wife.

28
00:02:12,319 --> 00:02:14,120
I also didn't expect

29
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,719
that the person I've been looking for
all these years

30
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:19,080
has become your fiancée.

31
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,639
You two know each other?

32
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,080
You go out first.

33
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,479
I need to talk to him.

34
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,240
She is not Wen Yanshu.

35
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:38,719
You've mistaken her.

36
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:40,719
She's about to marry me.

37
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:43,000
The past is the past.

38
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,960
Please don't disturb us anymore.

39
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,439
You are truly affectionate.

40
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:50,639
You found someone identical
as a replacement.

41
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:52,680
I am awed.

42
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:55,439
I will depart tonight.

43
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,840
It seems I won't be able

44
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,759
to attend your wedding.

45
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:01,719
I won't see you off.

46
00:03:05,152 --> 00:03:09,184
(Joy)

47
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,879
I prepared all these personally for you.

48
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:12,960
So?

49
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:14,080
Do you like them?

50
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:15,960
Yes.

51
00:03:16,192 --> 00:03:18,720
♪Tears suspended undecided♪

52
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,639
The dress is ready.

53
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,719
Try it now.

54
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:30,112
♪Isolated and cold♪

55
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:32,896
♪Gray hair reflected by falling snow♪

56
00:03:33,632 --> 00:03:36,960
♪Between all things,
hidden are the past years♪

57
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:41,024
♪Into my longing calamity♪

58
00:03:41,319 --> 00:03:42,800
You're in such a hurry to marry her.

59
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,919
Have you asked for her opinion?

60
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:47,319
She is destined to be with me.

61
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,199
There can be no more delay.

62
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,680
Aren't you afraid

63
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,919
she will regain her memory?

64
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:55,199
I am.

65
00:03:55,719 --> 00:03:56,520
I am afraid.

66
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,360
But I'm more afraid of her leaving.

67
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:02,439
Well then.

68
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,159
Staying away from Linzhao,

69
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:06,159
she might never remember the past again.

70
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,080
Stop talking.

71
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,240
(Joy)
(What exactly)

72
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,159
(is my memory?)

73
00:04:13,152 --> 00:04:17,312
(Joy)

74
00:04:28,448 --> 00:04:31,456
♪It's hard to part♪

75
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:35,399
I left a whistling arrow in your room.

76
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:37,639
If you want to leave here,

77
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,800
light it.

78
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:40,800
No matter where I am,

79
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:42,240
I will take you away.

80
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,720
I...

81
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:48,608
♪What is a touch of love♪

82
00:04:49,344 --> 00:04:52,672
♪Lowering eyes tenderly,
scattered glances♪

83
00:04:52,672 --> 00:04:56,864
♪Capturing the sad union♪

84
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:58,199
What did he say to you?

85
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,199
He was

86
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:02,959
saying goodbye

87
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:03,839
to me.

88
00:05:05,216 --> 00:05:08,864
♪Suddenly a drop of regret is lifted♪

89
00:05:08,864 --> 00:05:11,744
♪Melting the snow on my shoulders♪

90
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:15,776
♪Even if I can't express half of you♪

91
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,879
(But Shi'an is so good to me.)

92
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:20,000
(If I leave,)

93
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,800
(he will definitely be sad.)

94
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:26,399
Your Highness,

95
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,560
it's the auspicious time.

96
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,199
My lord,

97
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,600
wait no more.

98
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:53,240
The bridal sedan is off.

99
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,480
We should leave.

100
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,480
Even if it's by force,

101
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,000
I will take her away.

102
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,199
Wangyou?

103
00:06:25,439 --> 00:06:26,399
Yuan Jiyao?

104
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:29,600
Guards!

105
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:30,839
Pass on my order.

106
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:32,120
Seal the palace.

107
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,040
Yes.

108
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,279
Sorry.

109
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:41,480
It was a makeshift.

110
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:42,439
It's fine.

111
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,240
Thank you.

112
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,560
You only met me twice.

113
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,319
And you're leaving with me?

114
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:50,079
You are the Lord of Zishang, Linzhao.

115
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,360
People all say

116
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,360
you're a good person.

117
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,279
When we reach where no one is,

118
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,560
drop me off.

119
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,199
Drop you off?

120
00:07:01,759 --> 00:07:03,560
Did I say I would help you for free?

121
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,600
But

122
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:07,519
what if I don't have any money?

123
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,800
How about this?

124
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,160
Pay with yourself.

125
00:07:15,296 --> 00:07:18,400
♪It's no longer related to you♪

126
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,720
One thousand taels?

127
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,279
You're unscrupulous!

128
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:23,079
Just consider it

129
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:25,360
the fare for saving you out of the city.

130
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:28,519
But I was the crown princess just now.

131
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,320
Bai Ling,

132
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,120
where are we?

133
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,800
We're about to enter Linzhao.

134
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:37,439
Find a place without people to stop.

135
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:38,560
Yes.

136
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,079
Now that you said so,

137
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,600
why don't you go back

138
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,519
and remain a crown princess?

139
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,920
I was joking.

140
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,480
I can wash clothes, cook, clean,

141
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,720
and take care

142
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,480
of plants.

143
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,319
I'm all-rounded.

144
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:55,639
Really?

145
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:59,160
(But Wen Yanshu
would never plead with me.)

146
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:00,959
Get in.

147
00:08:16,256 --> 00:08:21,696
(Contract)

148
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,928
(20th Draw, Worst Sign:
Flower in the Mirror, Moon in the Water)

149
00:08:44,928 --> 00:08:45,600
(The rise and fall of fate is destiny.
All is void when waking up from dreams.)

150
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,720
The worst sign.

151
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,360
(Such a solemn expression)

152
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,440
(makes her look like Wen Yanshu.)

153
00:09:12,384 --> 00:09:12,960
(29th Draw, Best Sign)

154
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,039
(The new lotus buds. Fame will spread.)
The great fortune.

155
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,480
Man's will decides.

156
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,279
This place...

157
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:29,799
Does this place

158
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,279
feel familiar to you?

159
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:33,159
Do you remember anything?

160
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,159
No.

161
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,919
I just feel

162
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,679
this place is so special.

163
00:09:39,328 --> 00:09:42,560
♪No matter how much time has passed♪

164
00:09:43,159 --> 00:09:43,759
(My lord,)

165
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,639
(why do you set up Lover's Hill)

166
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:46,600
(like this?)

167
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:47,840
(I want to test)

168
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,799
(whether she is Yanshu.)

169
00:09:51,648 --> 00:09:53,344
♪But the ending is♪

170
00:09:54,208 --> 00:09:57,280
♪So ridiculous♪

171
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:02,304
♪It turns out nothing has changed♪

172
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:04,120
What beautiful fireflies!

173
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:09,472
♪If I see you again♪

174
00:10:09,664 --> 00:10:13,568
♪How should I choose♪

175
00:10:14,144 --> 00:10:15,968
♪You are♪

176
00:10:15,968 --> 00:10:19,744
♪Right before my eyes♪

177
00:10:21,088 --> 00:10:23,264
♪Why do I still need♪

178
00:10:23,616 --> 00:10:27,232
♪To pretend not to see you♪

179
00:10:28,256 --> 00:10:30,816
♪Why do we♪

180
00:10:30,912 --> 00:10:32,992
♪Dare not continue to write♪

181
00:10:32,992 --> 00:10:36,064
♪At the same time♪

182
00:10:36,064 --> 00:10:38,272
♪Do I have to♪

183
00:10:38,272 --> 00:10:41,504
♪Forget you again♪

184
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:51,320
Why did you fall asleep?

185
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,159
Shu.

186
00:11:01,856 --> 00:11:03,624
♪In the deserted world♪

187
00:11:03,846 --> 00:11:05,375
♪There are countless thoughts♪

188
00:11:05,878 --> 00:11:08,425
♪How many of them come true♪

189
00:11:09,801 --> 00:11:11,169
♪I've asked a thousand times♪

190
00:11:11,443 --> 00:11:13,229
♪Who is writing♪

191
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:17,053
♪Our mutual wishes♪

192
00:11:17,412 --> 00:11:19,082
♪When I open my eyes♪

193
00:11:19,263 --> 00:11:21,109
♪I see your smiling face♪

194
00:11:21,262 --> 00:11:24,724
♪Years pass by like fleeting water♪

195
00:11:25,219 --> 00:11:26,881
♪And the world keeps changing♪

196
00:11:27,056 --> 00:11:33,696
♪I wish to be with you
for the rest of my life♪

197
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,665
♪No fear of winds far away♪

198
00:11:36,836 --> 00:11:38,575
♪Between you and me♪

199
00:11:38,726 --> 00:11:42,487
♪Time is exchanged for moments♪

200
00:11:42,662 --> 00:11:44,169
♪If wishes can come true♪

201
00:11:44,330 --> 00:11:46,269
♪Between you and me♪

202
00:11:46,444 --> 00:11:49,504
♪Eternity is the end point♪

203
